---
[goal]
Ship the first shareable capsule layer for CRUMB so handoffs become visible, previewable, and resumable.

[context]
- CRUMB already supports structured handoffs, search, dreaming, sharing, and MeTalk compression.
- A capsule should preserve the CRUMB payload while generating a clean preview card and a compressed resume payload.
- The first version should target ChatGPT, Claude, Cursor, and Gemini without locking to any single vendor.

[constraints]
- Keep CRUMB v1.1 intact.
- Do not require a hosted backend.
- Keep the output easy to screenshot, share, and copy-paste.
END CRUMB
